text: Aï Keïta Yara is a Burkinabè actress. Her first movie was Sarraounia, where she played the queen the movie is named after. Sarraounia won several awards, and she was able to act in more movies and TV shows after that. == Other websites == * Aï Keïta Yara on IMDb * Aï Keïta Yara on Africultures (in French) == References == Category:African actors Category:Burkinabé people
